<br>
I lost 2k in JC items to lag.  These items I had transferred to my gf to chant them so I could craft them.  She had them at least a couple days and then we lost them to lag when she was giving the bars back to me.  He said the items had not been in my inventory, and was I sure I had them.  I said I had them for over a week.  After asking me a few more times if I was sure he said it was possible the increased staggering of backups with time would not reveal them in his records.  However my gf had them for 2 days at least and we managed to get him the day after the lag loss.  Thus the backup WOULD be full and accessible, however he could not be bothered to check HER inventory and just ignored us.<br>
